src:
VIXX's Leo to treat fans with a new single release on his birthday
07 Nov 2019, 20:50 by sl278



VIXX's Leo will be treating his fans to a new song on November 10.
The release date is even more meaningful as the release date is also his birthday. The cover art gives off aesthetic and artistic vibes and includes the title of the song, "All of me."
Stay tuned for more updates on Leo's release!
